      "writtenOn": "2020-07-06T02:27:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you mean creating and adding an independent data structure for Tast\u0027s internal use, so that we can add more fields to there freely?\n\nIIUC, what Tast want to do is:\n1. Emurate everything done for DUT hardware dependency filtering done by scheduler.\n2. Do some additional filtering if some dependency is not scanned by scheduler.\n\nHardwareFeature contains everything needed for #1 (because hwdeps CEL is evaluated with an environment having it). Therefore I thought we should use HardwareFeature, althought that is slice of the config.",
      "parentUuid": "b980fbe2_c713e2ca",
      "revId": "1e7db3b2782b354097cb2b589a3f3f72507c14a5",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
